imdb.plot outline: In A Liga a heterogeneous team of journalists, reporters and actors take off to live reality without prejudices. To show and explore a same fact from different angles including entertainment, irony, harshness, testimonies and drama. Each member of La Liga tries different focus on a same matter. They hunt for life stories without assumptions or accusations.
